text: Mee guu kumi labelaa nia henua o Israel huogodoo mai i di Ala Nnoonua o Hamath gaa tugi i bahi i ngeia di Tai Mmade i di bahi i ngaaga. Deenei di mee a Dimaadua, go di God o Israel, dela ne hagababa ang gi dana dangada hai hegau go soukohp Jonah, tama daane Amittai mai Gath Hepher.14.25 Jonah 1.1
